replies.body:
Broporo oooooon duty!{{summoner:31}} 

Since you said that it can sometimes load after you wait awhile, and that you've tried running as admin and reinstalling, it makes me think that this is more of a connection issue between your network and our servers. When it takes forever to load it could be having a really hard time establishing a stable connection to our servers, so it just sits.....and sits.....

Let's try going through our [Connection Guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) to see if we can get you set up with a more stable path to our servers.
